This paper is about improving the performance of neural machine translation (NMT) using relation networks (RN). The paper discusses the use of RN to refine the encoding representations of the source, which is a common problem in NMT. The paper also discusses the use of attention modules and decoders to improve the performance of NMT. Given these topics, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
